# This is a TEXT-ONLY library. Scanned page-image PDFs and any image/binary files
# must NOT live here — they belong in D:\repos\scans (Axcient-backed, off-repo).
# These patterns are a safety net so a stray binary can never be committed.

# Page-image / scanned PDFs and e-book binaries
*.pdf
*.epub
*.mobi
*.azw
*.azw3
*.djvu

# Images
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png
*.gif
*.bmp
*.tif
*.tiff
*.webp
*.svg
*.ico

# Audio / video
*.mp3
*.mp4
*.m4a
*.m4b
*.ogg
*.wav
*.avi
*.mov

# Archives / compressed
*.zip
*.gz
*.tar
*.7z
*.rar

# Stray scratch/temp files agents might leave
scratch_*
scratchpad_*
*.tmp
